<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WebPipe | Pipe from your servers to the browser!</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/app.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <nav class=container>
      <a href="/" class="nav-title">
        <img src="/static/logo.svg" class="webpipe-logo" />
      <h1 class=title>WebPipe</h1>
    </a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <section class=container>
      <h2>Pipe from your servers to the browser!</h2>
      <p class='tight-bottom'>
      Tail your log files
      </p>
      <pre><code>tail -f access.log | curl --upload-file - <%= @session_url %></code></pre>
      <p>
      View your logs in the browser here:
      <a href="<%= @session_url %>">
        <%= @session_url %>
      </a>
      </p>
    </section>
    <hr />
    <section class="container">
      <h2>FAQ</h2>
      <h3>Can someone else view my data?</h3>
      <p>
      The above URL has been generated just for you, it is 32 byte unique value and is guaranteed to be unique!
      However, if you send this URL to someone else, they too can view it, so share it responsibly!
      </p>
      <h3>How can I get a new token?</h3>
      <p>Just refresh the page to get a new token!</p>
      <h3>How much does it cost?</h3>
      <p>This is a free service, Please use it fairly.</p>
      <h3>How can improve this service?</h3>
      <p>
      Please <a href='https://github.com/hyperngn/webpipe/'>create a PR on our repository</a>❤️
      </p>
    </section>
    <hr>
    <section class="container">
      <h3>Send us a message</h3>
      <form action="https://liveformhq.com/form/725d00c0-264f-44db-ab71-046bac452965" method="POST" accept-charset="utf-8">
        <input type="hidden" name="_utf8" value="✓">
        <fieldset>
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email...">

          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea type="text" id="message" name="message"></textarea> <br />

          <input class="button-primary" type="submit" value="Send">
        </fieldset>
      </form>
    </section>
    <footer>
      <div class="container">
        <a href='https://hyperngn.com'>Hyperngn Inc</a> © 2020
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
